\langle \alpha x + y, z\rangle = \alpha \langle x, z\rangle + \langle y, z\rangle.
(\alpha x + y)^TAz.
(\alpha x + y)^TAz=(\alpha x)^TAz + y^TAz = \alpha x^TAz + y^TAz.
\alpha \langle x, z\rangle + \langle y, z\rangle.
